originalText.text: Dr. Williams has treated me for cosmetic as well as medical issues and I trust her implicitly for both; she's deeply knowledgeable, thoughtful, kind, and patient about explaining procedures. I have never felt rushed in her office. And I have recommended her to friends who have been as happy as I've been with our results. The best of the best.

originalText.text: Dr. Esther Williams is "the dermatologist's dermatologist"! Where to begin when discussing my dear dear friend and esteemed colleague Dr. Esther Williams?! She has a keen eye, a particularly skilled hand, a tremendous fund of knowledge and an even bigger heart. She is a kind and astute facial sculptor. What bigger compliment could I ever give to her than entrusting her with my face? (And posting about it publicly online)?! As a dermatologist who also practices cosmetic dermatology, she facilitates my own anti-aging -- allowing me to implement my aesthetic plans in the most natural way. Having known Dr. Williams since medical school and training together in residency, I can say with confidence that she has the "it factor." I trust her implicitly. My own patients often think I'm 10 years younger. Anyone treated by Dr. Williams would be so lucky! I recommend her in the highest regard.

originalText.text: Dr. Williams takes so much time to help me decide the most cost effective cosmetic options for meeting my goals. She’s conservative enough so that I never look “plastic” and people are always complementing my skin! Furthermore, she’s kind and gentle and honest. I can’t say enough great things about Dr. Williams and this practice as a whole.

originalText.text: I rarely post reviews online but my experience with Dr Williams has broken my usual routine. I went to see her after seeing several other dermatologists about acne/rashes on my forehead that were getting worse and I had an important public speaking event 10 days away. She took the additional time to ask several questions that the other doctors had not asked. Came to find out I had been giving myself steroid induced acne by overusing cortisone. After 5 months of trying everything- three days after my visit with Dr Williams my forehead was almost back to normal and a week later - better than it has been in years. She is now my go to dermatologist-highly recommended.
